nsanity that we call civilization the right path? I say no. Change comes slowly, but we may be running out of time.<br><br>I dream of the day when asked what race one is, the answer is: human.<br><br>I dream of the day when asked where one is from the answer is: Earth<br><br>I do not want us to end. I do not want death for all the mothers, sisters, brothers, fathers. We can be 10 times what we are now if we work together.<br><br>Our true enemy is war, death, violence, hunger, pestilence, war mongers, ... but most of all, ignorance. Make the leaders work harder toward this end. <br><br>I care about ALL of us. Please.........<br><br>Bruce A. Rhoades<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub80.ezboard.com/urhoadesb.showPublicProfile?language=EN>rhoadesb</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#F5F5DC>(2/18/01 12:22:42 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/funexplainedmysteriesesptheparanormal.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=65.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_exclamation_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: being off topic</span><hr size=1>    My apologies. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub80.ezboard.com/umiragezerooo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Miragezerooo</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_cyanspot.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 43<br> <font color=#F5F5DC>(2/18/01 8:07:52 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/funexplainedmysteriesesptheparanormal.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=65.topi